      <trans-unit id="12463" identifier="acf5c71bbd4603903bd9787829b512b1">
        <source>For this Sorting Network there can be up to three comparisons happening at
once, and the length of the network determines how long it would take to
complete all these comparisons.</source>
        <target>crwdns12463:0crwdne12463:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[14]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="12464" identifier="496d2baa0dbe7e5f54952d0ba89db419">
        <source>Although 12 comparisons need to be made when going through the network, the
network can be completed in the time it takes to an individual node to make 5
comparisons.</source>
        <target>crwdns12464:0crwdne12464:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /p[14]</note>
      </trans-unit>
